You might create something
like this Tableau dashboard.

121
00:04:46,325 --> 00:04:48,260
With interactive graphs that

122
00:04:48,260 --> 00:04:50,450
showcase multiple
views of the data.

123
00:04:50,450 --> 00:04:54,410
With this, users can change
location, date range,

124
00:04:54,410 --> 00:04:56,960
or any other aspect of
the data they're viewing

125
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:59,885
by clicking through different
elements on the dashboard.

126
00:04:59,885 --> 00:05:01,300
Pretty cool, right?

127
